(46,'第五届水利创新设计大赛','2021-03-15 14:00:00','龙子湖校区',15,120,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:23.0pt;\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">各学院：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.75pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.91;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">经学校研究决定，于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2019</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月下旬<span>举办我校第五届大学生水利创新设计大赛。现将大赛有关事项通知如下：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:黑体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">一、目的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体;color:black;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">为迎接</span><span style=\"font-size:\n14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;color:black\">第六届全国大学生水利创新设计大赛</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">，推动我校水利相关专业的教学改革，培养学生的创新能力、协作精神和理论联系实际的学风，加强学生动手能力的训练，提高学生解决实际问题的能力，</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:black\">强化实践育人环节，激励广大学生踊跃参加创新实践训练，在实训中<span>培养学生的协作精神、创新意识和实践能力，为我国水利事业建设和发展培养一批创新型人才。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:黑体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">二<code>、主题</code><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">华北水利水电大学第五届大学生水利创新设计大赛（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2019</span>年）的主题为“水<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>”，利用多种技术围绕“水<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>生活”、“水<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>生态”、“水<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>能源”、“水<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>节约”等进行实物作品的创新设计与制作，秉承可持续发展理念，注重节水优先、绿色生态、人水和谐及新技术的应用。作品须与大赛的主题和内容相符。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:黑体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">三、组织与领导</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">本次大赛由创新创业学院、教务处、学生处、校团委和水利学院联合举办。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">为了保证大赛的顺利开展，大赛成立华北水利水电大学水利创新设计大赛组委会，大赛的组织、评审与宣传等工作由我校水利创新设计大赛组委会和校团委、水利学院负责，日常工作由水利学院承担。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:黑体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">四、参赛条件与方式</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．参赛对象：</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\'=\"\">全校水利相关专业普通全日制本科在校大学生均可以个人或小组的方式，通过学院推荐参赛。每个参赛队（或每件作品）的学生人数不得超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\'=\"\">人，指导教师不超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\'=\"\">人。</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:black\">鼓励参赛学院在组织院级预赛的基础上，择优推荐参加本次大赛。</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">参赛作品由所在学院统一向组委会报名。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．参赛方式：按照大赛主题和内容的要求进行准备，完成作品的设计与制作，在获得学院推荐后，由各学院统一向大赛组委会提交下列材料：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）作品报名表；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）完整的设计说明书与图纸（包括纸质和电子文档）；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>）介绍作品功能的视频录像（不超过三分钟）；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）作品的实物模型或实物样机（入选全国大赛后提交）；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．作品要求：华北水利水电大学水利创新设计大赛作为我校创新教育中的一个实践教学环节，让学生结合某一命题开展广泛调研论证，充分发挥想象力和创造力，自行拟定设计方案，完成设计图纸，同时，由学生自行加工，完成实物作品的制作，达到全面培养学生创新设计能力和工程实践能力的目的。各学院可为参赛队聘请指导教师，但作品的选题、设计、分析和制作等项工作都应由学生自行组织与完成。所有作品必须为在校大学生的原创作品，不得侵犯他人的知识产权，不得将教师的科研成果作为学生作品参赛。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">实物作品体积不超过<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>立方米且最长方向尺寸不超过<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>米。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．参赛名额：各学院推荐的参赛作品数量不超过<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>件。</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:黑体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">五、大赛进程的时间安排<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．作品报名：各学院于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2019</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>日前将参赛作品报名表（见附件<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）及推荐参赛作品汇总表（见附件<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）各一份报送水利学院。同时发送报名表和汇总表的电子文档。参赛作品报名后，相关信息（包括作品名称、参赛学生、指导教师等）不得更改。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．作品提交：各学院于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2019</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span>日前将参赛作品的设计说明书按规定格式一式<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>份</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:black\">（双面打印）及</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">视频录像报送水利学院（龙子湖校区水利楼<span lang=\"EN-US\">2018</span>室），同时提交设计说明书电子版。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">作品实物及展板在入选全国大学生水利创新设计大赛后参赛报到时提交，</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;color:black\">其中展版以“易拉宝”为佳，面积不超过<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>米×<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>米。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">大赛时间：</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:black\">本次大赛将于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2019</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月下旬在水利学院举行，具体时间另行通知。</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;line-height:23.0pt;\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">六、评奖<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．奖项<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">本次大赛设立优秀作品奖、优秀指导教师奖和优秀组织奖三类奖项。其中优秀作品奖设一等奖、二等奖和三等奖各若干项。</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:black\">各奖项可以空缺。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．评审原则<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">由组委会负责本次大赛的评审。评审委员会本着“公平、公正、公开、科学、规范”的原则，通过设计资料审阅、现场答辩和实物演示等程序，从参赛作品的选题、方案设计、结构设计和制作等方面，对作品的合理性、创新性、实用性、先进技术的应用以及参赛队员答辩与作品现场演示情况等进行评审，确定优秀作品奖的归属。对于获一等奖作品的指导教师，颁发优秀指导教师奖。对竞赛组织工作成绩突出的学院颁发优秀组织奖。</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:28.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:23.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-weight:\nbold\">七、经费</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:26.9pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:1.92;line-height:23.0pt